additionalInfo.description:
This mapplet will parse a US phone number from string of text, validates the area code is valid for the US, and if it is valid,
returns the phone number in three different standard formats.  Also returns the status value (Valid / Invalid) and a
status description.

Tags: Integrity/Conformity, Accuracy, Conformity/Validity, USA

This mapplet validates the area code for US phone numbers.
Quality scores are:  0 - NULL or blank input
					10 - Invalid length
					40 - Valid length, Invalid Area Code
					95	- Valid length and Area Code

Tags: Accuracy, Conformity/Validity, Consistency

This mapplet standardizes the format of the phone string to have 
standard - (nnn) nnn-nnnn
dashes - nnn-nnn-nnnn
no spaces - nnnnnnnnnn
Phone_w_Extension  - (nnn) nnn-nnnn ext nnnnn

Tags: Standardize, USA, Customer, North America, Company, Phone

This maplet parses a phone number which may include an extension, that follows the standard format for the USA from a string of text into its own field.

Tags: Accuracy, Integrity/Conformity, PII, USA
